{
  "stem": "13469.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was only about six or seven years old, so we had to tell her exactly what to get, and give her the money kind of thing, and then send her into the shop.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were standing outside with our stars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We'd send her in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then she'd come back out again and say, what did you say what I had to get?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] How many do I have to get of this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And apparently, you know, everybody was watching, kind of thing, [LAUGHS] while we were manipulating Eve to buy things for us in these shops.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Can you remember doing this with her?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Richie told it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, I'd be interested whether Eve remembers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I shouldn't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it sounds all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Richie, of course, was born to this whole idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a-- scavenger, is one of the words, but an entrepreneur is another word, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, he was ideally suited to the camps and all the life that goes with it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had all these ideas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He and my mother, apparently, was good at it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, they apparently went out very often outside Amsterdam, which were not allowed to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they took the star off, Richie says, unbeknownst to my father, who wouldn't have liked it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took their star off and went outside Amsterdam to the farms and all that sort of thing and bartered for food with jewelry, or any other kind of things that we had.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was another law whereby-- there was a Jewish bank, called Lippmann, Rosenthal, in Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a big bank, Jewish bank, which was taken over by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all Jews had to hand over all their possessions, basically, to that bank.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
